original: Falck, Åke Erik Lennart, redaktör, Göteborg, f. 3/4/25 i Gbg av hälsov:-insp. John E. F. o. Andréa Edlund. — Studiex. v. Hvitfeldtska h. a. 1, i Gbg 44, stud. v. Gbgs högsk. Medarb. i olika Gbgstidn. 43-46, programtjänsteman v. Radiotjänst sed. 46.
translated: Falck, Åke Erik Lennart, editor, Gothenburg, born on April 3, 1925 in Gothenburg to health inspector John E.F. and Andréa Edlund. He completed his high school education at Hvitfeldtska h. a. 1 in Gothenburg in 1944, studied at Gothenburg University and worked as a contributor in various Gothenburg newspapers from 1943-1946. He became a program official for Radiotjänst in 1946 and married at an unknown date.
